=== Exits ===
There is exactly one exit from Sub-level '''Once Was Known, Now Is Forgotten''': Forgive.

The environment requires a "template" to maintain its physical stability. If a wanderer cannot reconcile their past, they become the new template, and their physical form is forfeited. The Custodian requires this template to manifest. By barring both the level and The Custodian from doing this, and the wanderer will be able to escape the level when it loses its stability and no-clipping zones begin to materialise.<div style="margin: 30px 0; font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 1.3em; background: #141008; padding: 12px; border: 1px dashed #6a5a40; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #b8a890;">FOLLOW THE POPPY TREES.</div>

