* '''Psychic Mass:''' Our sensors have detected localised "gravity spikes" corresponding with moments of intense regret. In this level, guilt is literally heavy.

<h2 style="border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; font-size: 1.3em; color: #111;">III. THE CUSTODIAN</h2>
