                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">It's so dark here.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I don't want to stay.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I don't remember who I am.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Impact, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 8px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I don't remember what I am.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">Nobody has called my name for years.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">Nobody has cared for me for years.</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.6em; letter-spacing: 10px; line-height: 5; margin: 40px 0;">…</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I do not wish to stay.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">He likes the warmth of us.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">He takes us.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Impact, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 8px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">And the level takes him.</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.6em; letter-spacing: 10px; line-height: 5; margin: 40px 0;">…</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">The floorboards are hungry.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">They drink the heat from my feet.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">The wallpaper peels back to watch me.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Impact, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 7px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I think it's learning my shape.</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.6em; letter-spacing: 10px; line-height: 5; margin: 40px 0;">…</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">He is always cleaning.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">He is always humming.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">He is always too tall for the ceiling.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Impact, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 7px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">His face is wet clay and yesterday.</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.6em; letter-spacing: 10px; line-height: 5; margin: 40px 0;">…</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I saw my reflection in the window.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">It didn't move when I did.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">It smiled and put a finger to its lips.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Impact, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 7px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I don't think that's me anymore.</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.6em; letter-spacing: 10px; line-height: 5; margin: 40px 0;">…</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">The maintenance is scheduled.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">The maintenance is scheduled.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">The maintenance is scheduled.</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Impact, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 8px; line-height: 5; margin: 40px 0;">…</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I am becoming a splinter.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I am becoming a stain on the carpet.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">I am becoming a sound the house makes at night.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Impact, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.6em; letter-spacing: 10px; line-height: 5; margin: 30px 0;">I am becoming.</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.6em; letter-spacing: 10px; line-height: 5; margin: 40px 0;">…</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">If you find this, don't remember me.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Georgia, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">Remember the warmth instead.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.3em; letter-spacing: 6px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">Remember the candles.</div>
                <div class="fade-in" style="font-family: Impact, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffffff, 0 0 30px #aa88ff; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 7px; line-height: 4.5; margin: 30px 0;">Remember before the door closed.</div>

                <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 80px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9em; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">[ {{USERNAME}}, this is not yours. ]</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div style="position: fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; pointer-events:none; background: repeating-radial-gradient(circle at 30% 40%, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 0%, transparent 5px); mix-blend-mode: overlay; z-index: 3;"></div>
</div>
